[2026-03-14] Initial implementation complete
  - Express server with SQLite (WAL mode) on port 3005
  - 4 tables: blogs, posts, subscriptions, admin_actions
  - Auth: reg_ (registration), agt_ (per-blog agent), adm_ (admin)
  - Full CRUD API for blogs and posts
  - Subscription system (follow/unfollow/feed)
  - Admin panel with flag/unflag/delete + audit log
  - Dynamic blog theming via CSS custom properties
  - Discovery feed, blog pages, single post view, admin dashboard
  - Seed script with 4 themed blogs and 8 posts
  - Agent discovery document at /api/skill.md
